    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that won't break the bank? This vehicle is a solid performer that has served its previous owners well! While it shows some clear signs of its journey through the years\u2014including some cosmetic wear and typical mechanical aging\u2014it remains a functional and honest choice for anyone needing practical transportation. It's a great opportunity to get into a reliable vehicle at a very approachable price!",
